  "detailed_description": "Far Star is a story-driven action-adventure game with Metroidvania influences. There is something fishy going on in this galaxy, but this won’t stop your intergalactic general services crew from doing their job using a varied set of skills, weapons and outfits.<br><br><strong>Your job will take you to various interesting places in the galaxy.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/40cc2a8e996db29efa92d8d42c47c55a.poster.avif?t=1751635344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/40cc2a8e996db29efa92d8d42c47c55a.webm?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/40cc2a8e996db29efa92d8d42c47c55a.mp4?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>With up to 4 members in your crew, you can swap them to choose the best one for the task in hand.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/17b5efb7488525fb267f0dadc113c887.poster.avif?t=1751635344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/17b5efb7488525fb267f0dadc113c887.webm?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/17b5efb7488525fb267f0dadc113c887.mp4?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Customize your characters to your likeness.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/214208ec9c5094ad57808d31a23171a3.poster.avif?t=1751635344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/214208ec9c5094ad57808d31a23171a3.webm?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/214208ec9c5094ad57808d31a23171a3.mp4?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Choose the best weapon for the job.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/fc95797116a461fce1ad7d915dc6cbee.poster.avif?t=1751635344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/fc95797116a461fce1ad7d915dc6cbee.webm?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/fc95797116a461fce1ad7d915dc6cbee.mp4?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Complete some light puzzles and mini-games.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/2989903f3b2258f19d8dcfc59d21e1f8.poster.avif?t=1751635344\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/2989903f3b2258f19d8dcfc59d21e1f8.webm?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1922990/extras/2989903f3b2258f19d8dcfc59d21e1f8.mp4?t=1751635344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The galaxy needs you!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai